---
import CornellNote from '../../../components/CornellNote.astro';
---

<html lang="ko">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<title>유형 05 - 난이도 [중] 연습</title>
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css">
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js"></script>
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js"></script>
		<style>
			body { background-color: #e0e0e0; margin: 0; padding: 20px; display: flex; justify-content: center; }
			.sol-button {
				display: inline-block; padding: 4px 12px; background: #fff8e1; color: #f57f17;
				border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: bold;
				margin-left: 10px; border: 1.5px solid #f57f17; transition: all 0.2s ease;
				white-space: nowrap;
			}
			.sol-button:hover { background: #f57f17; color: white; transform: translateY(-1px); }
			.question-card { background: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px; border: 1px solid #eee; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.02); }
			.question-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 15px; gap: 10px; }
			.formula-box { background: #fafafa; padding: 25px; border-radius: 12px; font-size: 1.3rem; text-align: center; }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<CornellNote title="유형 05. 무리식 극한 [중]" chapter="Level: Mid">
			<div slot="cues">
				<p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">🟠 [중] 핵심 포인트</p>
				<ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
					<li>분모에 루트가 있으면 <b>분모를 유리화</b>합니다.</li>
					<li>분자·분모 둘 다 루트면 <b>각각 켤레식</b>을 곱해봅니다.</li>
					<li>유리화 후 반드시 <b>영인자 약분</b>을 확인하세요.</li>
				</ul>
			</div>

			<section>
				<div class="type-section">
					<p style="margin-bottom: 25px; color: #666;">분모 유리화 또는 분자·분모 동시 유리화가 필요한 심화 단계입니다.</p>

					<!-- Q1 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0;"><b>Q1.</b> 다음 극한값을 구하시오.</p>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type05-mid/q1" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
						</div>
						<div class="formula-box">
							{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 3} \\frac{x-3}{\\sqrt{x+1}-2} $" }
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Q2 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0;"><b>Q2.</b> 다음 극한값을 구하시오.</p>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type05-mid/q2" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
						</div>
						<div class="formula-box">
							{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 0} \\frac{\\sqrt{x+4}-\\sqrt{4-x}}{x} $" }
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Q3 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0;"><b>Q3.</b> 다음 극한값을 구하시오.</p>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type05-mid/q3" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
						</div>
						<div class="formula-box">
							{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to 1} \\frac{\\sqrt{x+3}-2}{\\sqrt{x+8}-3} $" }
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div style="margin-top: 40px; display: flex; gap: 15px;">
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/types/type05/" style="color: #666; text-decoration: none;">← 핵심 문제로 이동</a>
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/problems-const/" style="color: #666; text-decoration: none;">목록으로 돌아가기</a>
				</div>
			</section>
		</CornellNote>

		<script is:inline>
			if (typeof window !== 'undefined') {
				document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", function() {
					if (typeof renderMathInElement === 'function') {
						renderMathInElement(document.body, {
							delimiters: [
								{left: '$$', right: '$$', display: true},
								{left: '$', right: '$', display: false}
							],
							throwOnError : false
						});
					}
				});
			}
		</script>
	</body>
</html>
